            "description": "Uploads and processes an image. Accepts multipart/form-data with field name 'image'. The backend will:\n- Validate file type (JPEG, PNG, WebP) and size (max 5MB)\n- Resize to thumbnail (150x150, 80% quality), medium (400x400, 85% quality), and large (800x800, 90% quality)\n- Optimize and convert to WebP (with JPEG fallback)\n- Upload to GCP Storage\n- Return URLs for all variants\n\nResponse includes:\n- originalUrl: URL for original image (or large if original is small)\n- thumbnailUrl: URL for 150x150 variant\n- mediumUrl: URL for 400x400 variant\n- largeUrl: URL for 800x800 variant\n- metadata: Information about the processed image\n\nRequires authentication via Bearer token."
